-- Government Must Go Back to `Square One' on Mining Tax, WA's Barnett Says
-- Jason Scott
-- 2010-06-25T02:54:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-25/government-must-go-back-to-square-one-on-mining-tax-wa-s-barnett-says.html

          
          
             Western Australia Premier Colin
Barnett, speaking to reporters in Perth today, said the new
federal government team under Julia Gillard needs to go back to
“square one” over its proposed resource super profit tax and
is hopeful the proposal will be abandoned.  
